__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.uv/
uv.lock

# Pipeline artifacts (regenerated by `just pipeline`).
# Slim CSV + summary in `output/` are committed; `tmp/` (full SQLite,
# rich analytical CSVs) is not. The rich JSONL audit trail is also
# regenerated by `just bake` and is too large for git, so it stays out
# too. Use `just bake` to refresh `output/` from a pipeline run.
tmp/
output/*.jsonl
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal

# Review artifacts (regenerated by `label_review.py`)
*.html
!docs/*.html
